# ChromeReader

This package provides access to local Chrome profiles data, including browsing history, bookmarks, and saved login data.

## Usage

```python
from ChromeReader import Profiler

profiler = Profiler() # Uses default User Data path

# Get first profile (Default)
profile = profiler.profiles[0]
print(profile) # Prints basic profile info

# Get last 10 visited urls from its history
hist_urls = profile.history.get_recent_urls(10)
print(*hist_urls, sep="\n")

'''

## Installing

```
pip install ChromeReader
```
